de.undercouch.citeproc.helper.tool

Class Option<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.undercouch.citeproc.helper.tool.Option<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - identifier type

    public class Option<T>
extends Object
    Command line tool option. Each option has an identifier that is used in the list of result values returned by OptionParser to link Values with Options.
    Author:
    Michel Kraemer
